{"tid":2082504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日媒：日本政府反對南韓加入G7 指責南韓對中共態度曖昧","createTime":"2020-06-28T05:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T11:36:52.000Z","uid":21470,"like":269,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"5f486fee8be146080c4347dbbcf3ce3ea215e918","tid":2082504,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"日媒指安倍政府反對南韓加入G7<br />\n28.06.2020 12:34<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，日本政府高官向美國政府傳達反對南韓加入七國集團峰會(G7)。報道指，日本認為南國的對華和對北韓的外交姿態與G7不一致，要求維持現有框架，美方回應指，總統特朗普將作出最終判斷。南韓政府對加入G7反應積極。分析指，日方的做法同時考慮要守住身為亞洲唯一G7成員國這外交優勢，有關表態可能導致日韓關係進一步倒退。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普上月曾批評G7框架非常落後，表明今年將邀請南韓、俄羅斯、印度、澳洲及巴西5國參加在美國召開的G7峰會，並將G7改名為G11或G12。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1322811&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1322811%26csid%3D261_367&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=95a27a0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1322811&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"2d8b49dffc4796d08c6462543e953e6ec58c2abb","tid":2082504,"uid":273703,"like":330,"dislike":1,"score":329,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"兩個之前奶共奶到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家歡迎鬥黃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e7fe10c1c8ff951be0b0a01318fffae04e3969","tid":2082504,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"2b865298ed1c94cda034d000e830e45f29ac53c2","tid":2082504,"uid":26283,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"quote":{"pid":"5f486fee8be146080c4347dbbcf3ce3ea215e918","tid":2082504,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"日媒指安倍政府反對南韓加入G7<br />\n28.06.2020 12:34<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，日本政府高官向美國政府傳達反對南韓加入七國集團峰會(G7)。報道指，日本認為南國的對華和對北韓的外交姿態與G7不一致，要求維持現有框架，美方回應指，總統特朗普將作出最終判斷。南韓政府對加入G7反應積極。分析指，日方的做法同時考慮要守住身為亞洲唯一G7成員國這外交優勢，有關表態可能導致日韓關係進一步倒退。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普上月曾批評G7框架非常落後，表明今年將邀請南韓、俄羅斯、印度、澳洲及巴西5國參加在美國召開的G7峰會，並將G7改名為G11或G12。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1322811&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1322811%26csid%3D261_367&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=95a27a0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1322811&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"第一次見人南韓會簡稱南國<br />\n個記者好有諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ce795149aa94229c1533bc71e8a0e19b138db2","tid":2082504,"uid":91397,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"日韓 揀邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813a66751225d9ffee3d96d95140d41af4075b4c","tid":2082504,"uid":22624,"like":44,"dislike":5,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"南泡同德國入支7算啦"},{"pid":"7f5733e9382c95e055a66a1e8991a53a7ccddb28","tid":2082504,"uid":52311,"like":70,"dislike":9,"score":61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:46:00.000Z","msg":"你日本又咪係一柒樣"},{"pid":"05ab8497ff7a37d603d32d0e95eca62e9bdd9f17","tid":2082504,"uid":36162,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:55:42.000Z","msg":"反支牌, 識得用其實好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ddff3c4fc7030e80d86a4f5904de263228a284","tid":2082504,"uid":13663,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"日本：南韓唔夠黃 我反共過佢好多"},{"pid":"b35745e65c170413149317ab86207e5cbbd7b339","tid":2082504,"uid":301989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2d8b49dffc479